  "detailed_description": "For over a millennia the land of Aforn has been under the tyrannical rule of the Dragon Lord.<br />\r\nAll attempts to overthrow him have led to near genocide, but the Dragon Lord's cruelty is <br />\r\nso great that despite the consequences another revolt is brewing. A revolt led by two souls <br />\r\nwho have lost everything to the Dragon Lord's senseless savagery.<br />\r\nWill you be able to lead them to victory, or will Aforn forever remain under his brutal rule?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA story rich experience with over a hundred cut scenes, Death To The Dragon Lord is a full<br />\r\nlength traditional JRPG which takes over 20 hours to complete.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStrategy Guide with walk-through and maps now available in the game folder.",
  "about_the_game": "For over a millennia the land of Aforn has been under the tyrannical rule of the Dragon Lord.<br />\r\nAll attempts to overthrow him have led to near genocide, but the Dragon Lord's cruelty is <br />\r\nso great that despite the consequences another revolt is brewing. A revolt led by two souls <br />\r\nwho have lost everything to the Dragon Lord's senseless savagery.<br />\r\nWill you be able to lead them to victory, or will Aforn forever remain under his brutal rule?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA story rich experience with over a hundred cut scenes, Death To The Dragon Lord is a full<br />\r\nlength traditional JRPG which takes over 20 hours to complete.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStrategy Guide with walk-through and maps now available in the game folder.",
